column2: How often do you usually shop fashion products?
column3: Your monthly spending on online shopping (£), if you shop fashion products seasonally or yearly, please use an estimated number.
column4: When you browse the shopping pages of fashion websites, do you do so with an obvious goal in mind? (e.g., knowing exactly what you want to buy)
column5: Factors you would consider when shopping fashion items online.
column6: To what extent would you choose to buy an unplanned fashion item because of the visual stimulation? (visual stimulation include web page design, Product Images and website UI etc.)
column7: Please rate your willingness in shopping fashion item on a complex but detailed web page, in this web page, textual descriptions are heavily weighted.
column8: If you lack willingness in shopping in this web page, can you specific why?
column9: Please rate your willingness in shopping fashion item on a simple but with less information web page, in this web page, graphical descriptions are heavily weighted.
column10: If you lack willingness in shopping in this web page, can you specific why?
column11: How much do you think the interactivity of the website (information to be logically presented, easy to use) plays a part in your online fashion shopping experience?
column12: How much do you think screen design on the website (i.e., colours, boxes, menus, navigation tools etc.) plays a part in your online fashion shopping experience?
column13: Please rate how much would you think an aesthetically pleasing web design and great web interaction design will make you trust/like the brand more?
column14: Please rate how much would you think that a good web design and interaction system is necessary for a successful online fashion shopping platform?
column15: To what extent do you think a personalized digital channel design would add to your purchase intention?
column16: How much do you willing to buy an item suggested by fashion websites based on their analyzed data?
column17: If you do, where would you expect the personalized content (e.g., item suggestion) to show up?
